<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA521_08_IH_0001</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_practice/js/ema521_01_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema521_08.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema521_08_ih_0001 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">채은이네 과수원에서 수확한 귤 3462개를 모두 상자에 담으려고 합니다. 한 상자에 100개까지 담을 수 있다면 최소 몇 상자가 필요한지 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">
            <span>알맞은 말이나 수에 ○표 하세요.</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="boolean_area mt_30">
            <span>3462개를 (</span>
            <div class="boolean_wrap" lang="y">
              <div class="boolean_box">
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="true">올림</button>
                ,
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">버림</button>
                ,
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">반올림</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <span class="ml-3">)하여 (</span>
            <div class="boolean_wrap" lang="y">
              <div class="boolean_box">
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">3400</button>
                ,
                <button type="button" data-answer-single="true">3500</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <span class="ml-3">)개로 생각합니다.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">수확한 귤을 남김없이 모두 담아야 하므로 올림하여 백의 자리까지 나타내면 3500입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">최소 몇 상자가 필요한가요?</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center mt_30">
            <div class="input_area">
              <span>(</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="35"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span lang="y">)상자</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">3500÷100=35이므로 최소 35상자가 필요 합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
